| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3406 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 918ce09c-f5f0-5c02-872e-1733bc9bb22b"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
